      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not roadworthy. It requires a complete mechanical overhaul, as the engine is non-functional and the transmission shows signs of failure. The exterior has extensive rust damage on the rocker panels and undercarriage, along with several large dents and failing clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is heavily torn, and several interior trim pieces are missing. This car is best suited as a parts donor or a total restoration project for a dedicated hobbyist.",
