      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example, maintained to an uncompromising standard. The vehicle remains in pristine condition, exhibiting flawless paintwork and an interior that retains its original showroom character. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a level of refinement that satisfies the most exacting standards. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of such distinguished quality.",
